title: Top Places to visit in Navsari, Gujarat
content: Navsari is a city and 9th biggest municipality of Gujarat and the administrative headquarters Navsari District of Gujarat, India. Navsari is also the Twin City of Surat, and only 30 km south of Surat. In 2016, Navsari ranked as the 16th biggest city of Gujarat state of india by population in 2011
